{"tid":882682,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【勵志】當年個同學飛咗個讀含管嘅男友，今日又復合","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T10:04:30.000Z","uid":36383,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d725131bfad133f4c604c31b3f0782714fb02a9","tid":882682,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"當年放完 jupas 冇耐，個同學 (下稱 X 小姐) 知道男友讀含管後就提出分手，話佢讀書唔成，衰過後門狗。個時佢仲話唔係大學生唔好同佢發展，佢塊西淨係比大學生屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔咗幾年之後，今日含大正名為恒大，個同學 ig 即刻影住沙田話咩『含大男友也不錯』。冇幾耐見到佢同條仔嘅合照，好似話一齊返冇半日已經有埋 bb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0b7bf448aad8edeeaa7b11ed267da98411ec59","tid":882682,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"個男友係你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dadf02be936c6dfc6c120a7459a284cd8972f9","tid":882682,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"我含萬歲萬歲萬萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09eb92236b235d40b5b1be0f9521b3d568805836","tid":882682,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀恒大嘅男人係時候翻身，追返初戀"},{"pid":"f5ce1a87284ff26d173a323ec3df5b082110116a","tid":882682,"uid":181505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"條女比我地城大人屌過幾百次"},{"pid":"64c004e017c9b69f15f1f6cc2972d823c6afa3dd","tid":882682,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09eb92236b235d40b5b1be0f9521b3d568805836","tid":882682,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/